      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable beauty that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, well-loved, and runs like a dream! Whether you\u2019re commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this ride is ready to go. It's got plenty of life left and is just waiting for the right person to take the wheel. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
