    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, providing an analog and engaging driving experience. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on structural integrity, including reinforced rear subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings to preserve the precision of the multi-link rear suspension. The engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with consistent compression, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator for improved thermal efficiency. This is a driver\u2019s car in solid condition, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
